'desc': [u'

Nuby Coolbite Fruit Teether (Orange) Price: Rs.175

Teethers are provided to infants who begin to develop their milk teeth. During this phase babies will feel pain and irritation on their gums owing to the emerging teeth. To relieve the pain and irritations the tiny tot will resort to biting that will put pressure on the gums which will soothe the ache to some extent. At such instances providing your bundle of joy with a good teether will prevent them from biting into anything and everything. The Nuby Coolbite Fruit Teethers have been designed with multiple textures to give your infant an array of surfaces to chew on.

The patented purIce gel that is integrated into the Nuby Coolbite Teether will help in retaining a cold temperature for a longer time after refrigerating. The cool temperature will help in relieving the ache in a much better way than a normal teether. These Nuby Teethers are designed and sized in such a way that they fit effortlessly into the baby’s tiny hands and allows them to hold the teether with a firm grip. You can use these Nuby Coolbite Teethers for your infants once they are three months old or above.
